title: DC Metro 'Other' Bus Line
name: DC Metro 'Other' Bus Line
description:
Other Bus Lines. This dataset contains other bus lines, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.

Data provided by several bus companies and organizations listed bus lines supplemental to WMATA bus data.

Acknowledgment of the DC Geographic Information Systems Program (DC GIS).
